Personaggio CORRETTO:
Photorealistic 26-year-old American woman long wavy blonde hair bright blue eyes flawless porcelain skin natural glow white silk robe gold earrings, bright minimalist bathroom marble countertop ring light soft professional beauty influencer aesthetic.

